ora solitaria y perdida, Sandra encuentra consuelo en la religión Wicca. Ella intenta realizar ceremonias Wiccas para atraer la buena fortuna a su vida. Pero cuando su falta de conocimiento sobre ese arte la lleva a abrir de forma involuntaria un portal paranormal, entonces Sandra debe combatir el mal que se ha desatado." type="movie" contentRating="PG-13" duration="2970000" originallyAvailableAt="2007-09-28T00:00:00Z" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://d31l2nn7dlh4li.cloudfront.net/amg27164/asset_artifacts/image/fetch_media/540da6b12c67ed25/AHaunting_2000x3000_SPANISH.png" title="Historias De Ultratumba S04E07: Hechizo" userState="0" year="2007"><Image alt="Historias De Ultratumba S04E07: Hechizo" type="coverArt" url="https://d31l2nn7dlh4li.cloudfront.net/amg27164/asset_artifacts/image/fetch_media/e9fbd6629607e961/AHaunting_S04E33_Spellbound.png"/><Image alt="Historias De Ultratumba S04E07: Hechizo" type="coverPoster" url="https://d31l2nn7dlh4li.cloudfront.net/amg27164/asset_artifacts/image/fetch_media/540da6b12c67ed25/AHaunting_2000x3000_SPANISH.png"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f308" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f308" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f308" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f308" slug="thriller" tag="Thriller" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1774762677" duration="2970000" endsAt="1774765647" id="69bf38cc4a800d9b2d844ccc" onAir="0" premiere="1" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1774783744" duration="2970000" endsAt="1774786714" id="69bf38cc4a800d9b2d844cd4" onAir="0" premiere="1" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1774804811" duration="2970000" endsAt="1774807781" id="69bf38cc4a800d9b2d844cdc" onAir="0" premiere="1" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1774825878" duration="2971000" endsAt="1774828849" id="69bf38cc4a800d9b2d844ce4" onAir="0" premiere="1" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video art="ht